{"PUFF":[{"def":"A sudden and single emission of breath from the mouth; hence, any sudden or short blast of wind; a slight gust; a whiff.","pos":""},{"def":"Anything light and filled with air.","pos":""}],"PUFF-LEG":[{"def":"Any one of numerous species of beautiful humming birds of the genus Eriocnemis having large tufts of downy feathers on the legs.","pos":""}],"PUFF-LEGGED":[{"def":"Having a conspicuous tuft of feathers on the legs.","pos":""}],"PUFFBALL":[{"def":"A kind of ball-shaped fungus (Lycoperdon giganteum, and other species of the same genus) full of dustlike spores when ripe; -- called also bullfist, bullfice, puckfist, puff, and puffin.","pos":""}],"PUFFER":[{"def":"One who puffs; one who praises with noisy or extravagant commendation.","pos":""},{"def":"One who is employed by the owner or seller of goods sold at suction to bid up the price; a by-bidder.","pos":""}],"PUFFERY":[{"def":"The act of puffing; bestowment of extravagant commendation.","pos":""}],"PUFFIN":[{"def":"An arctic sea bird Fratercula arctica) allied to the auks, and having a short, thick, swollen beak, whence the name; -- called also bottle nose, cockandy, coulterneb, marrot, mormon, pope, and sea parrot.","pos":""}],"PUFFINESS":[{"def":"The quality or state of being puffy.","pos":""}],"PUFFING":[{"def":"Puff adder (b), under Puff.","pos":""}],"PUFFINGLY":[{"def":"In a puffing manner; with vehement breathing or shortness of breath; with exaggerated praise.","pos":""}],"PUFFY":[{"def":"Swelled with air, or any soft matter; tumid with a soft substance; bloated; fleshy; as, a puffy tumor.","pos":""},{"def":"Hence, inflated; bombastic; as, a puffy style.","pos":""}]}